the more concepts I do that there's

00:13:23.187 --> 00:13:27.961
a lot of intuitive connections between
a lot of subjects but I think the

00:13:27.961 --> 00:13:31.939
1000 page text books and then you
know to some degree the beaurocracies

00:13:31.939 --> 00:13:33.945
of the standards making organizations.

00:13:33.945 --> 00:13:38.474
They kind of chop them up to a level
that you lose all of the intuition.

00:13:38.474 --> 00:13:42.283
