subject interactions and for me,

00:13:42.283 --> 00:13:46.240
what made math fun, what made
science fun was to really explore

00:13:46.240 --> 00:13:49.189
things and see how different
concepts were connected and what

00:13:49.189 --> 00:13:51.734
a formula is actually
saying about the universe.

00:13:51.734 --> 00:13:55.483
