formula is saying, and I also tell you

00:13:59.028 --> 00:14:02.697
what it's saying about the universe
generally, what are its implications,

00:14:02.697 --> 00:14:05.737
and also how did we get that formula.

00:14:05.737 --> 00:14:09.656
I don't just say memorize it and apply
it, and I think when you start learning

00:14:09.656 --> 00:14:12.837
that way, one it's a lot more fun
because we all actually do want

00:14:12.837 --> 00:14:16.402
to learn about the universe and it
actually builds a really, really strong

00:14:16.402 --> 00:14:19.346
foundation when you learn
more advanced topics.

